dct_title_s: Automobile routes from Fresno to San Francisco
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; F.T.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, drainage.
Indicates distances from Fresno and from Oakland via Haywards.
Numbered 76 in lower left corner and 27 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
